We would like to congratulate Serene Yeo, Desmond Soh, Sa Tay and Amarilynn Ngoh on being selected as our winners for this contest. We have sent you a PM with instructions on how to redeem your one-month unlimited pass with Push Pull Give!

Wohoo! Thanks to everyone for participating! :-) and congratulations to the lucky winners: Serene Yeo, Desmond Soh, Sa Tay, and Amarilynn Ngoh. If you have any questions, please also feel free to message us via facebook. :-) We are happy to have you on board and hope to see you very soon at one of our classes.

1. PUSH away carbo, practice self-discipline
2. PULL myself out of my comfort zone to embrace the challenges and reap the benefits of the exercises, practice diligence 
3. GIVE me my once upon a time toned body, throw in some awesome packs even better 🙂
